title: Smugglers 3
description:
Description:

     A Captivating Sci-fi Adventure

In the third part of the award winning science-fiction trading game you can play a greedy trader, an ambitious bounty hunter, a ruthless pirate, a mix of those or one of many other professions - the choice is entirely up to you.

Backed up by a crew of different kinds of crewmen (like droids or mercenaries) you can visit more than 75 planets in 25 systems in your attempt to gain favors with one of the four factions in the known galaxy.



Installation:

     1. Install the program.
     2. Overwrite original file with the included cracked one.
     3. Enjoy!
    [4. Apply addon-patch (optional)]
